See what life at Storey Creek has to offer

Residents can enjoy a variety of convenient amenities like a community swimming pool, clubhouse, fitness center, dog park and more.

See all amenities

Swimming Pool

Cool off on hot summer days or get a workout in at the community swimming pool

Clubhouse

The clubhouse is a great place to gather with neighbors and friends

Fitness Center

The onsite fitness center features a variety of equipment, allowing residents to get any kind of workout in

Tot Lot

The playground is ideal for allowing kids to play and interact with friends

Basketball Court

Shoot some hoops or enjoy a friendly pick-up game at the basketball court

Tennis Court

Work on your serve or play a match with friends at the onsite tennis courts

Volleyball Court

Enjoy the sand and sun while playing a friendly game at the community volleyball court

Located in the beautiful city of Kissimmee, FL. See what this city has to offer.

Storey Creek is close to local schools, restaurants, parks and an array of water-inspired activities at the 22,700-acre Lake Tohopekaliga, affectionately known as Lake Toho by the locals. Major thoroughfares such as SR 535, I-4 and US 192 make commutes to Orlando, Lakeland and Tampa a breeze.

Explore the neighborhood

Lake Tohopekaliga is renown for its diverse wildlife, including largemouth bass, ospreys, alligators and otters

Situated along the lake, Big Toho Marina serves casual breakfast fare along with tackle and bait for top-of-the-line bass fishing

Historic Downtown Kissimmee offers an array of shopping, dining and recreational options to cater to diverse tastes

Spend the day at Lakefront Park and enjoy walking paths, shaded picnic pavilions, playgrounds and a fishing pier off Lake Toho

AdventHealth Kissimmee provides award-winning medical care and services to its residents

Visit the community

Explore Storey Creek on a guided tour, either in-person or virtually, to learn more about floorplans, pricing, and availability.
